<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Day-4:-HIIT">Day 4: HIIT</h3>



<p>Day 4 is focused on HIIT or <em>high-intensity interval training</em>. HIIT is a cardiovascular workout designed to spike the heart rate using short bursts of maximum power with short recoveries. It has many benefits that apply to both<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/34281138/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"> physical and mental health</a>.</p>



<p>Among other advantages, HIIT is a highly effective cardiovascular workout. It efficiently raises the heart rate to improve aerobic fitness and increase calorie and fat-burning potential. It also positively impacts mental health and stress relief, which can be applied to many other aspects of daily life.</p>



<p>Below is a recommended HIIT routine.</p>



