<p>Day 7, the final day of the split, is primarily designed to serve as an <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29742750/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">active recovery day</a>. It incorporates movements to stretch and loosen the working muscles and joints for improved mobility and flexibility. They encourage muscle lengthening and reduce stiffness as well as stimulate blood flow for muscle repair and rebuilding.</p>



<p>The exercises below will help your muscles and joints reset and prepare for the next round of the challenge.</p>



